  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unwind with no time pressure, no scoring and no way to fail. Just tap patterns and watch as buildings, naturescapes and relaxing places are built for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/d82a552cb0b2c495a218267b123e582a.poster.avif?t=1727555363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/d82a552cb0b2c495a218267b123e582a.webm?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/d82a552cb0b2c495a218267b123e582a.mp4?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beautiful Environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tranquil Builds is all about the building. Step by step, brick by brick and tree by tree. Some builds are grand 1,000+ piece works of art while others are perfectly simple constructions. There's a selection to suit every curiosity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/6a16109fca6b5d5fdc8a7482bc2125fa.poster.avif?t=1727555363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/6a16109fca6b5d5fdc8a7482bc2125fa.webm?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/6a16109fca6b5d5fdc8a7482bc2125fa.mp4?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stress Free Gaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let go of the hustle and bustle of daily life. In Tranquil Builds, you can only succeed. Whether you tap 100 patterns a minute or just 1. Everything you do slowly but surely contributes towards your next masterpiece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed solely to be a relaxing experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buildings inspired by historic architecture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Machinery assembled bolt by bolt</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dioramas that tell intimate stories as they are constructed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deeply calming sound track</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unwind with no time pressure, no scoring and no way to fail. Just tap patterns and watch as buildings, naturescapes and relaxing places are built for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/d82a552cb0b2c495a218267b123e582a.poster.avif?t=1727555363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/d82a552cb0b2c495a218267b123e582a.webm?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/d82a552cb0b2c495a218267b123e582a.mp4?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beautiful Environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tranquil Builds is all about the building. Step by step, brick by brick and tree by tree. Some builds are grand 1,000+ piece works of art while others are perfectly simple constructions. There's a selection to suit every curiosity. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/6a16109fca6b5d5fdc8a7482bc2125fa.poster.avif?t=1727555363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/6a16109fca6b5d5fdc8a7482bc2125fa.webm?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2771980/extras/6a16109fca6b5d5fdc8a7482bc2125fa.mp4?t=1727555363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Stress Free Gaming</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let go of the hustle and bustle of daily life. In Tranquil Builds, you can only succeed. Whether you tap 100 patterns a minute or just 1. Everything you do slowly but surely contributes towards your next masterpiece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed solely to be a relaxing experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buildings inspired by historic architecture</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Machinery assembled bolt by bolt</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dioramas that tell intimate stories as they are constructed</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deeply calming sound track</p></li></ul>",
